Package users

Class StaffTest

java.lang.Object
testframework.BaseTest
users.StaffTest
public class StaffTest
extends BaseTest
Test class for the Staff entity. Tests functionality specific to Staff objects including: - Basic property getters and setters - Department ID handling - Staff queries by department - Information display formatting

Extends BaseTest to utilise the custom testing framework.
